about.summary: Simplifies the creation of Excel .xlsx files by providing a high level interface to writing, styling and editing worksheets. Through the use of 'Rcpp', read/write times are comparable to the 'xlsx' and 'XLConnect' packages with the added benefit of removing the dependency on Java.

name: r-openxlsx
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "4.1.5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-openxlsx
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/openxlsx_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/openxlsx/openxlsx_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 78a6e579dbbb767c3d658767965d4a561a0d763ce6b2b3e2053aa3a6f9507772

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp
    - r-rlang >=0.1.2
    - r-stringi
    - r-zip
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp
    - r-rlang >=0.1.2
    - r-stringi
    - r-zip

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('openxlsx')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('openxlsx')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://ycphs.github.io/openxlsx/index.html, https://github.com/ycphs/openxlsx
  license: MIT
  summary: Simplifies the creation of Excel .xlsx files by providing a high level interface to writing, styling and editing worksheets. Through the use of 'Rcpp', read/write times are comparable to the 'xlsx' and 'XLConnect' packages with the added benefit of removing the dependency on Java.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
